1
00:00:00,375 --> 00:00:04,500
There were prisoners from the town of Mansoura

2
00:00:08,083 --> 00:00:11,875
They were taken daily for interrogation and torture

3
00:00:12,125 --> 00:00:14,750
Then returned, and that continued for a while

4
00:00:15,208 --> 00:00:17,458
I saw their names on the wall

5
00:00:17,666 --> 00:00:19,875
And learned about their cases

6
00:00:20,166 --> 00:00:21,750
But I didn’t meet any of them because they were far from me

7
00:00:22,458 --> 00:00:24,625
I would hear the sounds of torture when they were taken

8
00:00:24,750 --> 00:00:26,291
But I didn’t know who they were

9
00:00:28,541 --> 00:00:34,750
Once, they took them out before the evening prayer

10
00:00:36,625 --> 00:00:38,041
They took them out one by one

11
00:00:38,208 --> 00:00:39,750
Asking what belongings they had

12
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,125
And if they wanted to send any message to their families

13
00:00:43,125 --> 00:00:45,291
Because the next day

14
00:00:45,708 --> 00:00:47,833
Was the day their sentences would be carried out

15
00:00:48,583 --> 00:00:49,625
Which was execution

16
00:00:50,125 --> 00:00:52,375
And crucifixion in the town of Mansoura

17
00:00:53,083 --> 00:00:55,708
They were sentenced on charges of highway robbery

18
00:00:56,791 --> 00:00:58,791
They were to face the <i>had al-hiraba</i> [punishment for banditry]

19
00:00:58,958 --> 00:00:59,958
Which is execution and crucifixion

20
00:01:00,833 --> 00:01:03,333
They didn’t sleep all night, praying to God

21
00:01:03,458 --> 00:01:05,833
They were taken the next morning

22
00:01:07,083 --> 00:01:08,500
At evening prayer time

23
00:01:08,958 --> 00:01:13,125
ISIS members brought us a newspaper they had issued

24
00:01:13,458 --> 00:01:15,875
It said they had carried out executions

25
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,333
Of eight people

26
00:01:18,291 --> 00:01:21,000
We stayed in shock for several days over what had happened
